OL,3,CMum lives in 'excruciating pain' after
OL,4,CKetamine destroys her bladder
OL,6,FThe warning comes after a new study by
OL,7,FKing's College London revealed that
OL,8,Fketamine related deaths have increased
OL,9,Fby 20-fold in the past decade.
OL,11,FAmber explained how Ketamine damages
OL,12,Fyour body
OL,14,FAmber says the addiction has affected
OL,15,Fher whole life, and more needs to be
OL,16,Fdone to inform young people of the
OL,17,Fdangers. Amber says she had no idea
OL,18,Fketamine could cause such serious
OL,19,Fdamage.
