OL,3,CMum lives in 'excruciating pain' after
OL,4,CKetamine destroys her bladder
OL,6,F"People say, 'You chose to do that,'
OL,7,Fbut I had no clue what ketamine could
OL,8,Fdo," she said.
OL,10,F"I never heard anything about it.
OL,11,FYoung people need to know this can
OL,12,Fruin your whole life."
OL,14,FDr Niall Campbell says Ketamine use is
OL,15,F"an epidemic"
