OL,3,CMum lives in 'excruciating pain' after
OL,4,CKetamine destroys her bladder
OL,6,FKetamine is often sold as white
OL,7,Fcrystalline powder. When snorted, its
OL,8,Fchemical breakdown products can
OL,9,Frapidly scar the bladder, shrinking it
OL,10,Fcausing unbearable pain and serious
OL,11,Fdamage.
OL,13,FWhile the research from King's College
OL,14,FLondon is staggering, doctors warn
OL,15,Fthat death is not the only danger.
