OL,3,CMum lives in 'excruciating pain' after
OL,4,CKetamine destroys her bladder
OL,6,FDespite being free from ketamine for
OL,7,Fmore than two years, Amber's symptoms
OL,8,Fremain extreme.
OL,10,F"I have to get up hours early just to
OL,11,Fcope with the pain," she said.
OL,13,F"At one point, I was spending more
OL,14,Fthan 10 hours a day in the bath,
OL,15,Fbecause hot water was the only thing
OL,16,Fthat eased it."
