OL,3,CMum lives in 'excruciating pain' after
OL,4,CKetamine destroys her bladder
OL,6,FShe says there is no medical
OL,7,Fsubstitute to help ketamine users come
OL,8,Foff the drug, unlike heroin addiction
OL,9,Ftreatment, making recovery especially
OL,10,Fdifficult.
OL,12,FIf she could speak to her 17-year-old
OL,13,Fself, Amber says she would say: "Don't
OL,14,Ftouch it. It's not worth it."
OL,16,FShe hopes that by speaking out, others
OL,17,Fwill think twice before trying the
OL,18,Fdrug.
